		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Drag wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Pretty cool, but does it use actual C64 hardware when in C64 mode, or is it an emulator?</div>
<br />It's a software emulator running on a 1.8GHz Intel Atom processor running the Ubuntu 10.04 LTS OS.
<br />
<br />Site: "Commodore OS 1.0, along with emulation functionality and classic game package, will be mailed to purchasers when available."
<br />
<br />Here's all the different version you can buy and what they include:
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.commodoreusa.net/CUSA_C64Select.aspx">http://www.commodoreusa.net/CUSA_C64Select.aspx</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
